        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-num">22</div><div><div class="faq-q">How does SAG-AFTRA Health Plan + Pension affect qualifying?</div><div class="faq-a">SAG-AFTRA Health Plan + Pension contributions from signatory employers documented through annual contribution statements. Pension benefit (after vesting) provides retirement income stream. Health Plan provides healthcare coverage during booking gaps. Both support continuity narrative.</div></div></div>
