        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-num">24</div><div><div class="faq-q">How does emerging commercial talent qualify?</div><div class="faq-a">Emerging commercial talent with limited booking history may qualify through FHA Conforming (3.5% down + lower credit accommodated) + future income trajectory documentation + SAG-AFTRA membership + agency representation + spouse income synthesis. First-time buyer pathway available.</div></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-num">25</div><div><div class="faq-q">When&rsquo;s the best time to apply as commercial talent?</div><div class="faq-a">Application timing varies. Stable commercial talent with recurring campaigns any time. Variable booking talent best post-tax-return-finalization (April-June) as prior year fully documented. Bank Statement Non-QM available year-round. Pre-qualification ahead of major campaign cycle compresses timeline.</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

